配分標準說明 Grading Description

平時作業 40%(Late assignments will not be accepted!)期中考120%(no make-up allowed)學期考120%(no make-up allowed)課堂討論 10%You should actively participate in discussion activities as well as share your ideas with the whole class.Discussion forum 10%After watching TED talk or videos from English Central in class, you are encouraged to write your opinions or feedback at the discussion forum at http://isee.scu.edu.tw/moodle/

